data.description: Welcome to your charming starter home nestled in the quaint small town of Ashland, between two bustling cities. This cozy abode features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and lots of personality! The main floor boasts all three bedrooms, a feature dining room wall, and a spacious kitchen, perfect for culinary adventures and gathering with loved ones. Downstairs, the basement offers endless potential for a versatile living area, home office, or recreational space. Step outside to the fenced backyard, ideal for hosting summer barbecues or cultivating your own garden oasis. Enjoy easy access to Ashland's bustling downtown, quaint shops, delectable dining options, and vibrant community events, with two major cities just a stone's throw away. Embrace the charm, convenience, and endless possibilities of small-town living in your new Ashland abode!
